Prepared for the "Trends in multi-omics data analysis for Microbial Ecology and
Biotechnology" Summer School (UFZ Leipzig).

The dataset in data/ (omics.db and the CSV exports) is entirely SYNTHETIC and was
generated by data/build_database.py; it does not correspond to any real samples.
